'''开放蠕虫'''（OpenWorm）是一项旨在从细胞层面在电脑上模拟[[秀丽隐杆线虫|秀丽隐杆线虫]]（Caenorhabditis elegans）的国际性[[开放科学|开放科学]]项目。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/05/05/nematode_fanciers_open_their_worm_to_a_kickstarter/ |title=nematode fanciers open their worm to a kickstarter |access-date=2014-10-17 |archive-date=2019-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191207102453/https://www.theregister.co.uk/2014/05/05/nematode_fanciers_open_their_worm_to_a_kickstarter/ }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://iospress.metapress.com/content/p61284485326g608/?p=5e3b5e96ad274eb5af0001971360de3e&pi=4 |title=Towards a virtual C. elegans: A framework for simulation and visualization of the neuromuscular system in a 3D physical environment. Palyanov A., Khayrulin S., Larson S.D. and Dibert A. (2012) In Silico Biology 11(3): 137-147 |access-date=2014-10-17 |archive-date=2014-04-22 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140422053822/http://iospress.metapress.com/content/p61284485326g608/?p=5e3b5e96ad274eb5af0001971360de3e&pi=4 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3900372/?tool=pmcentrez&report=abstract Current practice in software development for computational neuroscience and how to improve it. Gewaltig, M.-O., & Cannon, R. (2014).  PLoS Computational Biology, 10(1), e1003376. doi:10.1371/journal.pcbi.1003376]</ref>尽管该项目的长远目标是模拟整个[[秀丽隐杆线虫|秀丽隐杆线虫]]的全部959个细胞，第一阶段的计划是建立包含302个[[神经元|神经元]]和95个[[肌肉细胞|肌肉细胞]]的模型来模拟蠕虫运动。这种自底向上的模拟是开放蠕虫社区追求的目标。目前，此项目的物理引擎Sibernetic已经建好，神经[[连接组学|连接组]]和[[肌肉细胞|肌肉细胞]]也已创建为NeuroML格式。整个蠕虫的三维解剖模型可以通过浏览器自由查看。开放蠕虫项目也参与了“Geppetto模拟框架”的开发，这是一个为开发有机体的整体建模而创设的多重算法、多尺度的模拟平台。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://venturebeat.com/2014/04/30/openworm-is-going-to-be-a-digital-organism-in-your-browser/ |title=Openworm is going to be a digital organism in your browser |access-date=2014-10-17 |archive-date=2021-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211115154001/https://venturebeat.com/2014/04/30/openworm-is-going-to-be-a-digital-organism-in-your-browser/ }}</ref>

